"fundamentals/x5279a44ae0ab15d6:computational-thinking-with-variables\n"
"Course playlist: https://www.youtube.com/playlist?"
"list=PLSQl0a2vh4HDkbhG0sDW0b-VZXykEIAe5\n"
"\n"
"Khan Academy is a nonprofit organization with the mission of providing a "
"free, world-class education for anyone, anywhere. We offer quizzes, "
"questions, instructional videos, and articles on a range of academic "
"subjects, including math, biology, chemistry, physics, history, economics, "
